===假药===
该化合物已被欺诈性地用于治疗多种疾病，包括儿童自闭症<ref name=":0">{{Cite web|url=https://www.nbcnews.com/tech/internet/moms-go-undercover-fight-fake-autism-cures-private-facebook-groups-n1007871|title=Parents are poisoning their children with bleach to 'cure' autism. These moms are trying to stop it.|website=NBC News|language=en|access-date=2019-05-21|archive-date=2020-12-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201206214613/https://www.nbcnews.com/tech/internet/moms-go-undercover-fight-fake-autism-cures-private-facebook-groups-n1007871|dead-url=no}}</ref>。一些人也聲稱可飲用二氧化氯溶液以預防及治療[[2019新型冠状病毒|COVID-19]]<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.detroitnews.com/story/news/nation/2020/01/31/fake-news-corona-virus/41121279/|title=Fake news: Chlorine dioxide won’t stop coronavirus|website=Detroit News|language=en|access-date=2020-04-03|archive-date=2020-11-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201101024418/https://www.detroitnews.com/story/news/nation/2020/01/31/fake-news-corona-virus/41121279/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="#1"/><ref name="#2"/>。但需在水溶液下才能殺滅，也不能服用及接觸皮膚。一些人聲稱能殺滅[[2019新型冠状病毒|COVID-19]]的配戴式產品含有二氧化氯，但其效能存疑<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.xinhuanet.com/politics/2020-03/14/c_1125711681.htm |title=号称杀灭1米内99%病毒！神奇的“消毒卡”真有效吗？ |accessdate=2020-06-09 |archive-date=2020-08-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200807054930/http://www.xinhuanet.com/politics/2020-03/14/c_1125711681.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。{{Medical citation needed}} 被认为是治疗儿童自闭症的方法之一：用二氧化氯对儿童进行[[灌肠_(医学)|灌肠]]已经发现可以危及生命。 <ref name=":0" /> [[美国食品药品监督管理局|美国食品药品监督管理局]]（FDA）指出，二氧化氯的摄入或其他内部使用（除了可能在牙医监督下进行的口腔冲洗以外）对健康没有好处，并且出于任何原因都不得在身体内部使用<ref name="#3"/><ref name="FDA 20192"/>。 

二氧化氯的[[灌肠_(医学)|灌肠]]被认为可以治愈儿童时期的[[自闭症|自闭症]]，导致[[美国食品药品监督管理局|FDA]]投诉称其威胁生命， <ref>{{cite web |url=https://abc7news.com/news/group-of-socal-parents-secretly-try-to-cure-kids-with-autism-using-bleach/1578833/ |title=Group of SoCal parents secretly try to cure kids with autism using bleach |first=Lisa |last=Bartley |date=2016-10-29 |work=ABC 7 News |publisher=[[American_Broadcasting_Company|ABC]] |accessdate=2019-03-24 |archive-date=2020-11-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201110171835/https://abc7news.com/news/group-of-socal-parents-secretly-try-to-cure-kids-with-autism-using-bleach/1578833/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>甚至是死亡。<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.theguardian.com/society/2016/jul/13/fake-cures-autism-prove-deadly |title=The fake cures for autism that can prove deadly |first=Frances |last=Ryan |date=2016-07-13 |work=[[The_Guardian|The Guardian]] |publisher=[[Guardian_Media_Group|Guardian Media Group]] |accessdate=2019-03-24 |archive-date=2020-11-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201113223520/https://www.theguardian.com/society/2016/jul/13/fake-cures-autism-prove-deadly |dead-url=no }}</ref>
二氧化氯被标记为多种品牌名称，包括但不限于MMS，Miracle Mineral Solution和CD protocol。 <ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.vice.com/en_us/article/kwxq3w/parents-are-giving-their-children-bleach-enemas-to-cure-them-of-autism-311|title=The Parents Who Give Their Children Bleach Enemas to 'Cure' Them of Autism|author=|date=2015-03-12|website=vice.com|accessdate=2018-04-05|archive-date=2020-09-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200901014348/https://www.vice.com/en_us/article/kwxq3w/parents-are-giving-their-children-bleach-enemas-to-cure-them-of-autism-311|dead-url=no}}</ref>二氧化氯的医学特性没有科学依据，且FDA已警告不要使用二氧化氯。 <ref name="FDA 20192"/><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.fda.gov/NewsEvents/Newsroom/PressAnnouncements/ucm220747.htm|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110203232945/https://www.fda.gov/NewsEvents/Newsroom/PressAnnouncements/ucm220747.htm|url-status=dead|archive-date=2011-02-03|title=FDA Warns Consumers of Serious Harm from Drinking Miracle Mineral Solution (MMS)|date=2011-02-03|accessdate=2018-04-05|dead-url=no}}</ref>

=== 其它用处 ===
二氧化氯被用作氧化剂，以破坏[[废水|废水]]流中的[[酚|酚]]，并用于控制动物副产品（提炼）工厂的空气洗涤器中的气味。 <ref name="epa1999" />{{rp|4-34}} 它也可以用作汽车和船上的除臭剂，并被水活化并在船上或汽车中过夜放置，从而产生二氧化氯。

== 安全性 ==
二氧化氯是有毒的，因此需要限制其接触以确保其安全使用。 [[美国环境保护署|美国环境保护署]]已将饮用水中的二氧化氯的最高含量定为0.8毫克/升。<ref>{{cite web|title=ATSDR: ToxFAQs™ for Chlorine Dioxide and Chlorite|url=http://www.atsdr.cdc.gov/toxfaqs/tf.asp?id=581&tid=108|accessdate=2020-09-20|archive-date=2012-07-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120702160057/http://www.atsdr.cdc.gov/toxfaqs/TF.asp?id=581&tid=108|dead-url=no}}</ref>[[美国劳工部|美国劳工部]]的机构{{le|职业安全与健康管理局|Occupational Safety and Health Administration}}（OSHA）已将空气中二氧化氯的8小时{{le|允许暴露极限|Permissible exposure limit}}设置为（0.3 [[毫克|mg]]/[[立方米|m<sup>3</sup>]]）<ref>{{cite web |title=Occupational Safety and Health Guideline for Chlorine Dioxide |url=http://www.osha.gov/SLTC/healthguidelines/chlorinedioxide/recognition.html |accessdate=2012-12-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121204035804/http://www.osha.gov/SLTC/healthguidelines/chlorinedioxide/recognition.html |archive-date=2012-12-04 |url-status=dead |dead-url=no }}</ref>

2010年7月30日以及2010年10月1日，美国食品药品监督管理局都警告不要使用产品{{le|奇迹矿物补充剂|Miracle Mineral Supplement}}，又称 MMS。该产品必须按照说明进行配制产生二氧化氯。 MMS已被推销为多种疾病的治疗方法，包括HIV，癌症，[[自闭症|自闭症]]和痤疮。  FDA警告告知消费者，MMS可能对健康造成严重伤害，并表示已收到大量关于因脱水引起的恶心，腹泻，严重呕吐和危及生命的低血压的报道。<ref>{{cite web|archive-url=https://wayback.archive-it.org/7993/20170112005302/https://www.fda.gov/NewsEvents/Newsroom/PressAnnouncements/2010/ucm220747.htm|url=https://www.fda.gov/NewsEvents/Newsroom/PressAnnouncements/2010/ucm220747.htm|title=Press Announcements – FDA Warns Consumers of Serious Harm from Drinking Miracle Mineral Solution (MMS)|archive-date=2017-01-12|publisher=|accessdate=2020-09-20|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|archive-url=https://wayback.archive-it.org/7993/20171101112353/https://www.fda.gov/ForConsumers/ConsumerUpdates/ucm228052.htm|archive-date=2017-11-01|url=https://www.fda.gov/ForConsumers/ConsumerUpdates/ucm228052.htm|title='Miracle' Treatment Turns into Potent Bleach|publisher=U.S. Food and Drug Administration|date=2015-11-20|access-date=2017-12-06|dead-url=no}}</ref>此警告于2019年8月12日第三次重复，于2020年4月8日第四次重复，指出摄入MMS与喝漂白剂相同，并敦促消费者不要出于任何原因使用它们或将这些产品送给孩子。<ref name="FDA 20192"/>

